headline: Franklin Templeton Canada Introduces Franklin Core Equity Strategies
summary: Franklin Templeton Canada today introduced its Franklin Core Equity suite of Canadian, U.S. and international strategies. Franklin Canadian Core Equity Fund, Franklin U.S. Core Equity Fund and Franklin International Core Equity Fund will now be offered as an ETF series and series F for 10 basis points after the management fee waiver*.
